Sentencas: A cobalt-free layered perovskite oxide, GdBaFe2O5+x (GBF), was investigated as a novel cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs).
Titulo: Cobalt-free layered perovskite GdBaFe2O5+x as a novel cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Area-specific resistance (ASR) of GBF was measured by impedance spectroscopy in a symmetrical cell.
Titulo: Cobalt-free layered perovskite GdBaFe2O5+x as a novel cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The observed ASR was as low as 0.15 Omega cm(2) at 700 degrees C and 0.39 Omega cm(2) at 650 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Cobalt-free layered perovskite GdBaFe2O5+x as a novel cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: A laboratory sized Sm0.2Ce0.8O1.9 (SDC)-based tri-layer cell of NiO-SDC/SDC/GBF was tested under intermediate temperature conditions of 550-700 degrees C with humidified H-2 (similar to 3% H2O) as a fuel and the static ambient air as an oxidant.
Titulo: Cobalt-free layered perovskite GdBaFe2O5+x as a novel cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: A maximal power density of 861 mW cm(-2) was achieved at 700 degrees C.
Titulo: Cobalt-free layered perovskite GdBaFe2O5+x as a novel cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The electrode polarization resistance was as low as 0.57, 0.22, 0.13 and 0.08 Omega cm(2) at 550, 600, 650 and 700 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Cobalt-free layered perovskite GdBaFe2O5+x as a novel cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The experimental results indicate that the layered perovskite GBF is a promising cathode candidate for IT-SOFCs.
Titulo: Cobalt-free layered perovskite GdBaFe2O5+x as a novel cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells
